<P>Bo&s;ton: Printed by SAMUEL ETHERIDGE, Sold by B. LARKIN, W. SPOTSWOOD, THOMAS &amp; ANDREWS, D. WEST, E. LARKIN, J. WEST, and W. P. BLAKE. 1795.</P>
