<HEAD>CHAP. XIV.</HEAD>
<EPIGRAPH>
<Q><L>"Have you the heart? When your head did but ach&punc;</L>
<L>"I knit my handkerchief about your brows,</L>
<L>"And with my hand at midnight held up your head;</L>
